dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.compound.CompoundAspectCompoundResourceDetails
dataStructure.description:
This class is a concrete class that defines the semantics of aggregating CompoundResources into a CompoundResource using the CompoundResourceAspects aggregation. In the DEN-ng system view, OCL is used to mandate the presence of at least one PhysicalResource and at least one LogicalResource. The aggregation of CompoundResources are optional.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: CompoundAspectCompoundResourceDetails
